# 🔥 WTF! SAMGYUP POS — App Layout Guide
# Complete Screen-by-Screen Text Layout (PRD2-Aligned)

> **Aligned to:** PRD2.md (4-module architecture)
> **Source:** Extracted from actual component source files
> **Purpose:** Reference guide for all text, labels, headings, and UI elements

---

## COMPLETE USER FLOW

```
Splash (Login) → [PIN Modal if Manager] → Top Bar (Navigation)
    ├── Floor Plan View ──→ Running Bill ──→ Add Item Modal ──→ Checkout / Receipt
    ├── Kitchen Queue View (Kitchen Staff only)
    ├── Stock Management (Manager only)
    │     ├── Meats Tab
    │     ├── Sides Tab
    │     └── Pantry Tab + Audit Log Sidebar
    ├── Menu Manager (Manager only)
    └── Reports View
          ├── X-Reading
          ├── Z-Reading
          ├── Analytics
          ├── Voids
          ├── SC/PWD Log
          ├── Leftover Log
          ├── Audit Trail
          └── eSales Export
```

---

## MODULE 1: CORE SAMGYUP POS & SYSTEM FOUNDATION

---

### SCREEN 1: SPLASH / LOGIN

**File:** `Splash.jsx`

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│              🔥                       │
│          WTF! SAMGYUP                │
│         RESTAURANT POS               │
│           ─── (divider)              │
│                                      │
│  YOUR NAME                           │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ Enter your name...           │    │
│  └──────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                      │
│  ROLE                                │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │ 👤 Staff                     │    │
│  │    Servers & Cashiers        │    │
│  ├──────────────────────────────┤    │
│  │ 👑 Manager                   │    │
│  │    Admin Access              │    │
│  ├──────────────────────────────┤    │
│  │ 🍳 Kitchen Staff             │    │
│  │    BOH Team                  │    │
│  └──────────────────────────────┘    │
│                                      │
│  [ START SHIFT ] or [ CONTINUE → ]   │
│                                      │
│  hint: manager pin is 1234           │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Text Elements:**
- Header: `🔥` (icon), `WTF! SAMGYUP` (brand), `RESTAURANT POS` (subtitle)
- Label: `YOUR NAME`, `ROLE`
- Input placeholder: `Enter your name...`
- Role cards:
  - `👤 Staff` — `Servers & Cashiers`
  - `👑 Manager` — `Admin Access`
  - `🍳 Kitchen Staff` — `BOH Team`
- Button: `START SHIFT` (staff/kitchen) / `CONTINUE →` (manager)
- Footer hint: `hint: manager pin is 1234`

---

### SCREEN 1B: PIN MODAL (Manager Login & Overrides)

**File:** `PINModal.jsx`

```
┌──────────────────────────┐
│           🔐              │
│       Manager PIN         │
│     {reason text}         │
│                           │
│      ● ● ○ ○  (dots)     │
│                           │
│    [ 1 ] [ 2 ] [ 3 ]     │
│    [ 4 ] [ 5 ] [ 6 ]     │
│    [ 7 ] [ 8 ] [ 9 ]     │
│    [   ] [ 0 ] [ ⌫ ]     │
│                           │
│     [ VERIFY PIN ]        │
│        ← Back             │
│       or Cancel           │
└──────────────────────────┘
```

**Text Elements:**
- Header: `🔐`, `Manager PIN`, `Manager PIN Required` (on login)
- Dynamic: `{reason}` — e.g., "Void order item", "Void entire table"
- Buttons: `VERIFY PIN`, `← Back` (login), `Cancel` (override)
- Number pad: `1–9`, `0`, `⌫`

---

### SCREEN 2: TOP BAR (Global Navigation)

**File:** `App.jsx`

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ 🔥  WTF! SAMGYUP  POS  │ [⬜ Floor] [📦 Stock] [📖 Recipes] [🍽️ Menu] [📊 Reports] │ {occ} occ  {free} free │ 👤 {Name} (role) [Logout] │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Navigation Items (role-based):**

| Key       | Icon | Label     | Visible to        |
|-----------|------|-----------|--------------------|
| `floor`   | ⬜   | Floor     | Staff, Manager     |
| `kitchen` | 🍳   | Kitchen   | Kitchen            |
| `stock`   | 📦   | Stock     | Manager            |
| `recipes` | 📖   | Recipes   | Manager            |
| `menu`    | 🍽️   | Menu      | Manager            |
| `reports` | 📊   | Reports   | Staff, Manager     |

**Status Chips:**
- `{N} occ` (orange) — occupied tables
- `{N} free` (green) — available tables
- `{N}kg servable` (green, stock view only)

**Stock Alert Bar (Manager only):**
- `⚠ Low Stock:` + per-item badges:
  - `❌ {item name} ✕` (out of stock)
  - `⚠ {item name} ✕` (low stock)
- `👁 {N} hidden` (toggle for dismissed alerts)

---

### SCREEN 3: FLOOR PLAN VIEW

**File:** `FloorMap.jsx`

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  FLOOR PLAN  ─────────  ● Available  ● Occupied  ● VIP  ● Bar│
│                                                               │
│  ┌────────────────────────────┐    ┌──────────────────┐       │
│  │     MAIN DINING            │    │  VIP / PRIVATE   │       │
│  │                            │    │                  │       │
│  │  ┌─────┐  ┌─────┐         │    │  ┌────────┐      │       │
│  │  │ T1  │  │ T2  │  ...    │    │  │ VIP1   │      │       │
│  │  │ 2p  │  │ 2p  │         │    │  │ 8p     │      │       │
│  │  │⏱ 45m│  │     │         │    │  │⏱ 1:20  │      │       │
│  │  │₱2,394│  │     │         │    │  │₱12,450 │      │       │
│  │  └─────┘  └─────┘         │    │  └────────┘      │       │
│  │                            │    ├──────────────────┤       │
│  │                            │    │     BAR          │       │
│  │                            │    │  ┌─────┐┌─────┐  │       │
│  │                            │    │  │BAR1 ││BAR2 │  │       │
│  │                            │    │  └─────┘└─────┘  │       │
│  ├────────────────────────────┘    └──────────────────┘       │
│  │  🍳 KITCHEN COUNTER   🚪 ENTRANCE                          │
│  └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
│                                                               │
│  WINDOW (rotated label on left edge)                          │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Labels (fixed on map):**
- `FLOOR PLAN` (section header)
- `MAIN DINING`, `VIP / PRIVATE`, `BAR`, `WINDOW`
- `🍳 KITCHEN COUNTER`, `🚪 ENTRANCE`

**Legend:**
- `● Available` (green), `● Occupied` (orange), `● VIP` (purple), `● Bar` (cyan)

**Per Table (occupied):**
- `{T-label}` (e.g., T1, VIP1, BAR1)
- `{seats}p` (capacity)
- `🔥` (fire icon)
- `⏱{elapsed}` / `⏱{elapsed} ⚠` (timer with warning)
- `{₱bill}` (running bill total)
- `Unli Pork` / `Unli Beef` / `Unli Pork & Beef` (package label above table)
- `+{merged tables}` (merge indicator)

**Merge/Transfer Indicators:**
- `🔀 Merging from {label} — tap occupied table to merge into`
- `🔄 Transferring from {label} — tap empty table`

**Context Menu (tap occupied table twice):**
- `{T-label} Actions` (header)
- `📋 View Orders`
- `👥 Change Pax`
- `🔀 Merge Table` (manager)
- `🔄 Transfer Table` (manager)
- `🗑 Void Table` (manager, red)

**Empty Side Panel (no table selected):**
- `📋` (large icon)
- `No Table Selected`
- `Tap an occupied table to view orders.`

