### SCREEN 4: RUNNING BILL (Side Panel)

**File:** `RunningBill.jsx`

```
┌──────────────────────────────┐
│  ➕      {T-label}  👥 {N} pax│
│  ADD           ✕ (close)     │
│  {emoji} {Package Name} ·    │
│  ⏱ {elapsed} ⚠ OVERTIME      │
│  + {merged labels}           │
│                              │
│  ⚠ Session exceeded 90 min! │
│  Consider checkout.          │
│                              │
│  Order List:                 │
│  ┌──────────────────────────┐│
│  │ {name} {weight}g   PKG   ││
│  │ {note} · {time}   ₱{$$}  ││
│  │                     ✕     ││
│  │ {name}         FREE       ││
│  │ {name}         VOID       ││
│  │  voided by {name}         ││
│  └──────────────────────────┘│
│                              │
│  🍽️ No orders yet            │
│  Tap "➕ Add" below to start │
│                              │
│  {N} items · 🥩 {N}g         │
│  cost ≈₱{N} (manager only)  │
│  BILL           ₱{total}    │
│                              │
│  [🗑 Void] [💳 Checkout] [🖨 KOT]│
└──────────────────────────────┘
```

**Text Elements:**
- Header: `{T-label}`, `👥 {N} pax`
- Package line: `{emoji} {Package Name}` or `No package — à la carte`
- Timer: `⏱ {elapsed}` with states: normal / `⚠` warning / `⚠ OVERTIME`
- Alert: `⚠ Session exceeded 90 minutes! Consider checkout.`
- Alert: `⚠ Session approaching time limit. Consider checkout soon.`
- Empty state: `🍽️`, `No orders yet`, `Tap "➕ Add" below to start`
- Order tags: `PKG`, `FREE`, `VOID`, `{weight}g`
- Footer: `{N} items · 🥩 {N}g`, `cost ≈{₱N}`, `BILL ₱{total}`
- Buttons: `🗑 Void`, `💳 Checkout`, `🖨 KOT`
- Floating button: `➕ ADD`

---

### SCREEN 5: ADD ITEM MODAL

**File:** `AddItemModal.jsx`

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  LEFT PANEL                          │  RIGHT PANEL      │
│  ➕ Add to Order                     │  Pending Items     │
│  {emoji} {Package} · {N} pax        │  Review items      │
│                                      │  before pushing    │
│  TABS:                               │  to the main bill. │
│  [🎫 Package][🥩 Meats][🥬 Sides]   │  👥 {N} Pax  ✎     │
│  [🍜 Dishes][🥤 Drinks]             │                    │
│  FREE — inventory tracked / PAID ITEM│  {item list}       │
│                                      │  ┌────────────┐   │
│  CONTENT varies by tab:             │  │ {name}      │   │
│                                      │  │ {weight}g   │   │
│  * Package: cards with price/pax    │  │ [-] 150g [+]│   │
│  * Meats: grid with weighing        │  │ Fine-tune   │   │
│  * Sides: grid with stock           │  │ [==slider==]│   │
│  * Dishes: sub-tabs + grid          │  └────────────┘   │
│  * Drinks: grid with pricing        │                    │
│                                      │  PENDING TOTAL     │
│                                      │  ₱{total}          │
│                                      │                    │
│                                      │ [Undo] [⚡ CHARGE] │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Header:**
- `➕ Add to Order`
- `{emoji} {Package Name} · {N} pax` or `{N} pax · No package selected`

**Tabs:**
- `🎫 Package`, `🥩 Meats`, `🥬 Sides`, `🍜 Dishes`, `🥤 Drinks`

**Sub-header:** `FREE — inventory tracked` (package/meat/sides) or `PAID ITEM` (dishes/drinks)

**Package Tab:**
- Warning: `⚠ Selecting a new package will replace the current one ({name})`
- Per package card:
  - `{emoji} {name}`, `{description}`
  - `{₱price}/pax`, `= ₱{total}`
  - `✓ {N} sides, {N}g initial meats`
  - `✓ ACTIVE` (current)

**Meat Tab:**
- Empty: `🎫`, `Select a package first to add meats`, `[Go to Packages]`
- Per meat card: `{name}`, `≈{₱cost}/100g` (manager), stock status:
  - `Not in package`, `Out of stock`, `⚠ Low — {N}g`, `{N}g available`
  - `FREE · tap to weigh`
- Weight entry: `← Back to meats`, `{name}`, `{N}g available · FREE with {pkg}`
  - Preset buttons: `100g`, `150g`, `200g`, `250g`, `300g`, `500g`
  - Input placeholder: `Enter grams...`
  - Button: `ADD {N}g {meat name}`

**Sides Tab:**
- Per card: `{name}`, `{stock} {unit} · FREE`

**Dishes Tab:**
- Sub-tabs: `Snacks`, `Rice`, `Noodles`, `Soup`
- Per card: `{name}`, `₱{price}`

**Drinks Tab:**
- Per card: `{name}`, `₱{price}`

**Pending Sidebar (right):**
- Header: `Pending Items`, `Review items before pushing to the main table bill.`
- Pax button: `👥 {N} Pax ✎`
- Empty: `🍽️`, `No pending items`
- Package item: `{N} pax`
- Meat item: `{name}`, `{N}g total`, `Fine-tune Weight`, slider `-50g` to `+50g`
- Side/dish/drink item: `{name}`, `₱{price}` or `FREE`, qty `[-] {N} [+]`
- Footer: `PENDING TOTAL ₱{total}`
- Buttons: `Undo`, `⚡ CHARGE ({N})`

