### SCREEN 6: CHECKOUT / RECEIPT MODAL

**File:** `ReceiptModal.jsx`

```
┌──────────────────────────────┐
│  🧾 {T-label} — Checkout     │
│  {N} pax · {Package} · {time}│
│  {OR number}                 │
│                              │
│  Line Items:                 │
│  {name} ({weight}g)  ₱{price}│
│  {name}              free    │
│                              │
│  📊 {N}g meat · est. cost    │
│  ₱{N} · margin ≈₱{N}        │
│  (manager only)              │
│                              │
│  DISCOUNT                    │
│  [None][Senior 20%][PWD 20%] │
│  [Promo 10%]                 │
│  ┌────────────┐┌───────────┐ │
│  │Customer name││ID number  │ │
│  └────────────┘└───────────┘ │
│                              │
│  LEFTOVER PENALTY (₱200/pax) │
│  ┌───────────────────┐       │
│  │Leftover grams     │ □ Ovr │
│  └───────────────────┘       │
│  +₱{N} penalty ({N} pax×₱200)│
│                              │
│  Subtotal           ₱{N}    │
│  Discount          −₱{N}    │
│  Leftover penalty  +₱{N}    │
│  ─────────────────────────  │
│  TOTAL              ₱{N}    │
│                              │
│  VATable Sales      ₱{N}    │
│  VAT (12%)          ₱{N}    │
│  VAT-Exempt Sales   ₱{N}    │
│                              │
│  [💵 Cash][💳 Card][📱 GCash]│
│  ┌───────────────────┐       │
│  │ Cash tendered...  │       │
│  └───────────────────┘       │
│  CHANGE: ₱{N}               │
│                              │
│  [ ✓ CONFIRM & CLOSE TABLE ] │
└──────────────────────────────┘
```

**Text Elements:**
- Header: `🧾 {T-label} — Checkout`, `{N} pax · {Package} · {time}`, `{OR-YYYYMMDD-XXXX}`
- Manager info: `📊 {N}g meat · est. cost ₱{N} · margin ≈₱{N}`
- Section: `DISCOUNT`
  - Buttons: `None`, `Senior 20%`, `PWD 20%`, `Promo 10%`
  - Inputs: `Customer name *`, `ID number *`
- Section: `LEFTOVER PENALTY (₱200/PAX)`
  - Input: `Leftover grams (0 = none)`
  - Checkbox: `Override` (manager)
  - Text: `+₱{N} penalty ({N} pax × ₱200)`
- Totals: `Subtotal`, `Discount`, `Leftover penalty`, `TOTAL`
- Tax: `VATable Sales`, `VAT (12%)`, `VAT-Exempt Sales`
- Payment: `💵 Cash`, `💳 Card`, `📱 GCash`
  - Input: `Cash tendered...`
  - Computed: `CHANGE: ₱{N}`
- Button: `✓ CONFIRM & CLOSE TABLE`

