- Empty state: `😴`, `No active tables`, `Kitchen queue is clear`
- Per table card header: `{T-label}`, `{N} pax · {Package}` or `{N} pax · à la carte`, `⏱ {elapsed}`
- Sections: `🥩 MEATS — {N}g total`, `🍜 DISHES & DRINKS`, `🥬 SIDE REQUESTS`
- Empty card: `No actionable orders yet`

