│  🥬 Sides & Accompaniments · Tap a card to restock or deduct        │
│  ┌────────────────┐                                                  │
│  │ [image]  {icon} │                                                 │
│  │ {name}          │                                                 │
│  │ [████░░] {N}    │                                                 │
│  │ Par: {N}        │                                                 │
│  └────────────────┘                                                  │
│                                                                      │
│  ══ PANTRY TAB ══                                                    │
│  {CATEGORY NAME}  (uppercase, e.g. STAPLES, SAUCES, PRODUCE)        │
│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────┐                            │
│  │ {icon} {name}    OUT/LOW             │                            │
│  │        [████░░] {N} {unit}           │                            │
│  │               par: {N}  ₱{N}/{unit}  │                            │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────┘                            │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Audit Log Sidebar (toggle):**
```
┌────────────────────┐
│  🕐 Audit Log      │
│  {N} entries    ✕   │
│                    │
│  No stock changes  │
│  yet               │
│                    │
│  Grouped entries:  │
│  ┌────────────────┐│
│  │ {title}        ││
│  │ ● {userName}   ││
│  │ {time}         ││
│  │ {itemName}     ││
│  │ +{N} g / -{N} g││
│  │ {category}     ││
│  │ {note}         ││
│  │ 📷 View Attach.││
│  └────────────────┘│
└────────────────────┘
```

**Text Elements:**
- Header: `📦 Stock Management`, `Meat, sides, and pantry inventory`
- Toggle: `🕐 Audit Log ▸` / `🕐 Audit Log ◂`
- Sub-tabs: `🥩 Meats`, `🥬 Sides`, `📦 Pantry` (with badge counts for low items)
- Stat pills: `{N}kg Servable Meat`, `{N} Low Sides`, `{N} Low Pantry`
- Meat section: `🥩 Meat Inventory · All weights in grams`
  - Tags: `✓ OK`, `✓ LOW`, `✓ OUT`
  - Labels: `Servable / Par Level`, `Cost: ₱{N}/kg`, `Servable value: ₱{N}`
- Sides section: `🥬 Sides & Accompaniments · Tap a card to restock or deduct`
  - Labels: `Par: {N}`
- Pantry section: Category headers (e.g., `STAPLES`, `SAUCES`, `PRODUCE`, `SUPPLIES`)
  - Tags: `OUT`, `LOW`
  - Labels: `par: {N}`, `₱{N}/{unit}`
- Audit: `🕐 Audit Log`, `{N} entries`, `No stock changes yet`, `📷 View Attachment`

