## MODULE 3: EXPENSES RECORDING (Future — PRD2 Spec)

> **Note:** The Expenses module is specified in PRD2 but not yet implemented in the prototype.
> The following is the PRD2 specification for reference.

**PRD2 Expense Entry Interface Requirements:**
- Secure, PIN-protected dropdown forms for categorizing daily expenses
- Categories: electricity, gas, labor, supplies, others
- Owner PIN required for all expense entries
- Automatic logging of recurring fixed costs (rent, subscriptions)
- Daily and monthly expense-vs-sales summaries

---

