- Button: `Execute Z-Reading now`
- Stat cards: `Gross Sales`, `Voids / Refunds`, `Discounts (SC/PWD)`, `VATable Sales`, `VAT Amount (12%)`, `VAT Exempt Sales`, `Net Sales`, `Grand Acc. Total`, `Z-Counter`, `Beginning OR`, `Ending OR`, `Total Txns`
- Section: `Today's Transactions`
- Empty: `📋 No transactions today`

