## SHARED UI COMPONENTS

### Open Table Form
**File:** `OpenForm.jsx`
- Title: `Open {T-label}`
- Default pax: 2, range 1-12

### Change Pax Form
**File:** `PaxForm.jsx`
- Title: `Change Pax`
- Shows current pax, allow adjustment

### Modal Wrapper
**File:** `MWrap.jsx`
- Generic wrapper with `{title}` and close button `✕`

### Chips & Badges
**File:** `Chip.jsx`, `UserBadge.jsx`, `Tag.jsx`, `TCM.jsx`
- Chip: `{label}` with color dot
- UserBadge: `{emoji} {Name}` with role color (Staff=blue, Manager=purple, Kitchen=orange), `Logout` button
- Tag: colored label
- TCM: text-in-circle micro-badge (e.g., `CASH`, `GCASH`, `SENIOR`, `PWD`)
